ch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\"\n"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Square.png", "id": "666948167247977", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610715_666948170581310_6397857849105774023_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ohYJN0h2QXwQ7kNvgEjiLZ7&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHvyT0-DqZzl5Ckpz1mAy3AMdfoNA69noHWSfswuOypw&oe=67139F9C"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Logo.png", "id": "1248298442180126", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75299157_1248298445513459_4217660042221025690_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=her0MGOzTh8Q7kNvgE7B2TQ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDub3bCclm_L7VVL7ZItEdmZfnXQxfi3tUqXuDEfvyo5g&oe=6713AC30"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "944988136020255", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75557066_944988142686921_2558777294337714060_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=c44NG1Ags2sQ7kNvgHgl8DG&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD4MvY87TIr3AtpjQnt2JvAAI1Er208H0-ZQNHkkfcUuA&oe=6713A527"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Portrait.png", "id": "821345848684633", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_821345852017966_7561255947146577431_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=U2wqwFPGzC0Q7kNvgEtwbRl&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBDKGyUdy0Fq4hFSKhldPM9HSpMAgvgT9k027rhzRb_RQ&oe=67137FCE"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Landscape.png", "id": "7796862827